3C/h2>\u003C/h2>\u003C/column>\u003Ccolumn id=iwx283 class=\"gc-6 gc-sm-8 gc-xs-10\">\u003Cimg src=\"https://firebasestorage.googleapis.com/v0/b/genos-ec52a.firebasestorage.app/o/pages%2Fhome%2Fteam.jpg?alt=media\" id=iewdwu>\u003C/column>\u003C/div>\u003Csection id=YA5FEVOEVWYCEXvO class=\"complex-section spacer\">\u003C/section>\u003Csection id=BRK1ENKU47gsqxHg class=complex-section>\u003Cdiv id=lu6RgyxszVN9fh9A class=\"grid grid-large complex-section-grid\">\u003Ccolumn id=pZsfLecv3wkfHI0L class=gc-12>\u003Ch2 id=iqahec class=h3>The Human Glycome Project\u003C/h2>\u003C/column>\u003C/div>\u003Cdiv id=ioig2x class=\"grid grid-large\">\u003Ccolumn id=igtfu7 class=\"gc-9 KYVq6mdbafW8YhmG gc-sm-12\">\u003Cp id=i4ixbk>\u003Cspan>\u003C/span>Ambiciozna znanstvena inicijativa usmjerena na mapiranje cijelog ljudskog glikoma, koji obuhvaća sve glikane prisutne u ljudskom tijelu.\u003Cbr>\u003Cbr id=ixctfh>\u003Ca href=http://localhost:5173/ id=ipzu0e title=https://www.youtube.com/@HumanGlycomeProject/featured target=_blank>Pogledajte najnovije videozapise\u003C/a> \u003Cspan id=ic54x3>o istraživanjima i inovacijama u glikobiologiji.\u003C/span>\u003C/p>\u003C/column>\u003C/div>\u003C/section>\u003Cdiv id=i2fola class=\"grid grid-large\">\u003Ccolumn id=9MiFxV1VrUEEumpz class=\"gc-12 cta-arrows\">\u003Cimg src=\"https://firebasestorage.googleapis.com/v0/b/genos-ec52a.firebasestorage.app/o/pages%2Farrows%2Farrow-right-blue.svg?alt=media\" id=dH3AJJky8RByCcRw class=\"arrow-big hide-xs\">\u003Cimg src=\"https://firebasestorage.googleapis.com/v0/b/genos-ec52a.firebasestorage.app/o/pages%2Farrows%2Farrow-right-blue.svg?alt=media\" id=QD3k1YDaaQQXfefq class=\"arrow-big hide-xs\">\u003Cimg src=\"https://firebasestorage.googleapis.com/v0/b/genos-ec52a.firebasestorage.app/o/pages%2Farrows%2Farrow-right-blue.svg?alt=media\" id=atl0rMWdgUhjtl89 class=arrow-big>\u003Ca id=ip6cuv href=https://human-glycome.org/ target=_blank class=hover-underline>human-glycome.org\u003C/a>\u003Cimg src=\"https://firebasestorage.googleapis.com/v0/b/genos-ec52a.firebasestorage.app/o/pages%2Farrows%2Farrow-left-blue.svg?alt=media\" id=panBLNlsTxXEQekC class=arrow-big>\u003Cimg src=\"https://firebasestorage.googleapis.com/v0/b/genos-ec52a.firebasestorage.app/o/pages%2Farrows%2Farrow-left-blue.svg?alt=media\" id=agSwYeDGfhqZ1wxS class=\"arrow-big hide-xs\">\u003Cimg src=\"https://firebasestorage.googleapis.com/v0/b/genos-ec52a.firebasestorage.app/o/pages%2Farrows%2Farrow-left-blue.svg?alt=media\" id=QatGefcauW3QoQA3 class=\"arrow-big hide-xs\">\u003C/column>\u003C/div>\u003Csection id=QxEoDGRj8XIIJmT7 class=complex-section>\u003Cdiv id=IGJLBSqkr2je3xQU class=\"grid grid-large complex-section-grid from-science-to-product\">\u003Ccolumn id=YeBbQQSOxfxUcTeR class=gc-9>\u003Ch2 id=Ki38WEjEwrTvDEj7 class=\"h2 complex-section-title from-science-to-product-title\">\u003Cspan>\u003C/span>\u003Cspan id=igcter>From science to product:\u003Cbr>\u003Cb>\u003Cspan id=inabnk>GlycanAge\u003C/span>\u003C/b>\u003C/span>\u003C/h2>\u003C/column>\u003Ccolumn id=J8mNKwmUc6gGtLJw class=gc-3>\u003Cimg src=\"https://firebasestorage.googleapis.com/v0/b/genos-ec52a.firebasestorage.app/o/pages%2Fabout%2Fkit.png?alt=media\" id=uX0uQP8XAFtUyi7t class=\"complex-section-image from-science-to-product-img\">\u003C/column>\u003Ccolumn id=csbWHQFtkslPAvTn class=\"gc-9 KYVq6mdbafW8YhmG gc-sm-10 gc-xs-12\">\u003Cp id=ilhfa8>\u003Cspan>\u003C/span>GlycanAge je testni komplet za određivanje biološke dobi (i usluga za poboljšanje zdravlja). Djeluje mjerenjem broja protuupalnih i pro-upalnih glikana vezanih za IgG.\u003Cbr>\u003Cbr id=ir1ety>\u003Cspan id=iavar6>Cilj mu je pomoći ljudima povećati broj protuupalnih, a smanjiti broj pro-upalnih glikana. Genos već više od 20 godina istražuje glikane kao biomarkere te danas služi kao središnji centar za analizu krvnih uzoraka GlycanAge testa.\u003C/span>\u003C/p>\u003C/column>\u003C/div>\u003C/section>\u003Cdiv id=i6imn1 class=\"grid grid-large\">\u003Ccolumn id=N8MJ9hXMJingWa75 class=\"gc-12 cta-arrows\">\u003Cimg src=\"https://firebasestorage.googleapis.com/v0/b/genos-ec52a.firebasestorage.app/o/pages%2Farrows%2Farrow-right-green.svg?alt=media\" id=UhkdOwaoY92aluuj class=\"arrow-big hide-xs\">\u003Cimg src=\"https://firebasestorage.googleapis.com/v0/b/genos-ec52a.firebasestorage.app/o/pages%2Farrows%2Farrow-right-green.svg?alt=media\" id=sgoMmtnawQ4Jdow5 class=\"arrow-big hide-xs\">\u003Cimg src=\"https://firebasestorage.googleapis.com/v0/b/genos-ec52a.firebasestorage.app/o/pages%2Farrows%2Farrow-right-green.svg?alt=media\" id=BskE9ebAKRZ09QoK class=arrow-big>\u003Ca data-pblink id=gjiUJpY6sRTyfbQK href=https://glycanage.com/ >\u003C/a>\u003Ca id=ixv4is href=https://glycanage.com target=_blank>glycanage.com\u003C/a>\u003Cimg src=\"https://firebasestorage.googleapis.com/v0/b/genos-ec52a.firebasestorage.app/o/pages%2Farrows%2Farrow-left-green.svg?alt=media\" id=WLa2EKU7yBFuiDW0 class=arrow-big>\u003Cimg src=\"https://firebasestorage.googleapis.com/v0/b/genos-ec52a.firebasestorage.app/o/pages%2Farrows%2Farrow-left-green.svg?alt=media\" id=2hwekRwRk26wZ3BW class=\"arrow-big hide-xs\">\u003Cimg src=\"https://firebasestorage.googleapis.com/v0/b/genos-ec52a.firebasestorage.app/o/pages%2Farrows%2Farrow-left-green.svg?alt=media\" id=comjYKTbjRRspgXM class=\"arrow-big hide-xs\">\u003C/column>\u003C/div>\u003Csection id=cb4wWhbea4jEqXLt class=\"cta-request spacer\">\u003Cdiv id=Rbq0AnbmP662y5AF class=\"grid grid-large cta-request-grid\">\u003Ccolumn id=NQVg8GqZHOp1Y8Yh class=gc-12>\u003Ch2 id=1KElwK6h2Ue7gnbV class=\"cta-request-text h4\">\u003Cspan>\u003C/span>\u003Cspan>\u003C/span>\u003Cspan id=DgjUBKlw8sBQxTVd>Ako ste zainteresirani za suradnju s nama ili korištenje naših usluga, besplatno pošaljite zahtjev, a mi ćemo zakazati sastanak kako bismo razgovarali o vašim idejama.\u003C/span>\u003C/h2>\u003C/column>\u003Ccolumn id=hCMD0uhdE2OjFhlA class=gc-12>\u003Ca data-pblink id=zkfmHXgxQVgLxkmW href=/kontakt class=\"cta-big cta-y